{"tid":1052231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美准醫生處方氯胺酮鼻噴劑 治療嚴重抑鬱患者","createTime":"2019-03-08T07:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T07:22:44.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"72b552f21541fcd944988724cab5712ddb95905e","tid":1052231,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"美准醫生處方氯胺酮鼻噴劑 治療嚴重抑鬱患者<br />\n<br />\n美國醫學界周二批准執業醫生處方俗稱K仔的氯胺酮類藥物，治療起碼對2種抗抑鬱藥無效的嚴重抑鬱症病人，希望讓他們的情緒問題快速地得以緩解。<br />\n<br />\n美國食品藥品管理局（FDA）批准醫生處方含艾氯胺酮（esketamine）並名為「Spravato」的鼻噴劑，由醫療保健產品公司強生（Johnson &amp; Johnson）研製。現時的抗抑鬱藥如「百憂解」（Prozac）的藥理是針對控制情感的神經傳導物質血清素（serotonin），患者可能要服食數星期甚至數月才有作用，但「Spravato」可令患者即時感到有效，而且紓解抑鬱的程度更大。<br />\n<br />\n報道指艾氯胺酮比氯胺酮更易於使用，「Spravato」含的是低劑量艾氯胺酮，由於可能令人上癮及有副作用，必須由執業醫生處方並要在病人用藥後觀察2小時，及後也要長期跟進以確保安全。<br />\n美國有740萬名成年人有抗藥性抑鬱問題，哥倫比亞大學（Columbia University）的學者曼恩（John Mann）解釋，短時間內起作用對於抑鬱症患者而言很重要，因為他們病發時非常無助及痛苦，如果試過一種藥物無效，醫生就可以立即為病人轉藥。<br />\n<br />\n科學家也一直研究迷幻蘑菇內的賽洛西賓（Psilocybin）及狂喜內的成份是否可當成治療抑鬱症的藥物，引來不少爭議，今次艾氯胺酮獲當局「開綠燈」，可能為有關爭論帶來新發展。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190306/59335613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335613&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e93bea22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335613&h=c1f00f0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190306/59335613</a>"},{"pid":"ac6fb5ff23428b602cbf7dcfc4586ca07ba87c04","tid":1052231,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"索k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6057656ab92279bad7846edcf0cfc062986732d","tid":1052231,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"連登毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxbusiness.com/foxbusiness.com/content/uploads/2019/03/0/0/Spravato.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa57.foxnews.com%2Fstatic.foxbusiness.com%2Ffoxbusiness.com%2Fcontent%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F0%2F0%2FSpravato.jpg%3Fve%3D1%26tl%3D1&h=32d30235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09ac8ff0a91733586581f945dbba588ab08487e","tid":1052231,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要去老美睇醫生"},{"pid":"b7ace23eca4b90861fca1f88ac14b0acc1ef6bf2","tid":1052231,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"講真個個道友唔多唔少都有抑鬱症架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81028866f493545a0cd8f7b74710fc5d7fafc19","tid":1052231,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"美國已經有adderall仲要食呢d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350d1248d7d9ead50296e3f5103f4356f3a86dc3","tid":1052231,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"氯胺酮本身就係藥物黎,, 第一日出現時就係藥物<br />\n<br />\n同鴉片一樣, 鴉片一開始係醫學用途<br />\n<br />\n係D人濫用先會被稱為毒品, 其實係「濫用藥物」<br />\n<br />\n有乜值得大驚小怪？"}]}